arts.ttl: Eredivisie Round Up: AZ defeat Ajax as Utrecht win again
arts.sum: Below is a round up of Sunday’s Eredivisie action. Groningen 0-0 PEC Zwolle Groningen and PEC Zwolle played out a 0-0 draw in the Euroborg. The hosts had the better chances in the first half but Thijs Oosting couldn’t convert two good opportunities that came his way.
